### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000

###

### Register New User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123",
  "phone": "9876543210"
}

###

### Login Admin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@kanbags.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Login Buyer
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "buyer123"
}

###

### Verify Token (Replace TOKEN with your JWT)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/products

###

### Get Products with Filters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/products?category=office&material=leather&minPrice=1000&maxPrice=5000&sortBy=price-low

###

### Get Featured Products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/products/featured

###

### Get Single Product (Replace with actual product ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/products/PRODUCT_ID

###

### Create Product (Admin only - Replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/products
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Leather Bag",
  "category": "office",
  "material": "leather",
  "price": 2999,
  "originalPrice": 3999,
  "description": "Beautiful new leather bag",
  "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553062407-98eeb64c6a62",
  "images": ["https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553062407-98eeb64c6a62"],
  "stock": 50,
  "featured": false
}

###

### Get Active Coupons
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/coupons/active

###

### Validate Coupon
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/coupons/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "LAUNCH50",
  "cartTotal": 2500
}

###

### Get Active Advertisements
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/advertisements/active

###

### Submit Bulk Inquiry
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/inquiries/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rajesh Kumar",
  "email": "rajesh@business.com",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "businessName": "Kumar Retail",
  "businessType": "retailer",
  "quantity": "100 pieces per month",
  "message": "Looking for wholesale rates"
}

###

### Place Order (Replace TOKEN and PRODUCT_ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "products": [
    {
      "productId": "PRODUCT_ID",
      "name": "Executive Briefcase",
      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553062407-98eeb64c6a62",
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 3499
    }
  ],
  "shippingAddress": {
    "name": "John Doe",
    "phone": "9876543210",
    "street": "123 Main Street",
    "city": "Kanpur",
    "state": "Uttar Pradesh",
    "pincode": "208001"
  },
  "total": 3499,
  "discount": 0,
  "shippingCost": 0,
  "finalTotal": 3499,
  "paymentMethod": "cod"
}

###

### Get User Orders (Replace TOKEN and USER_ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders/user/USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Get All Orders (Admin - Replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Get Single Order (Replace TOKEN and ORDER_ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders/ORDER_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Cancel Order (Replace TOKEN and ORDER_ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders/ORDER_ID/cancel
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Changed my mind"
}

###

### Update Order Status (Admin - Replace TOKEN and ORDER_ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders/ORDER_ID/status
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "shipped",
  "trackingNumber": "TRK123456789"
}

###




